		<title>What To Do If You Have a Traffic Ticket Case During Coronavirus Quarantine.</title>
		<link>https://www.ticketclinic.com/blog/traffic-ticket-case-coronavirus</link>
				<comments>https://www.ticketclinic.com/blog/traffic-ticket-case-coronavirus#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2020 17:10:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[TC Admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[All]]></category>
